I use the default pick screen
I use the default pick screen
the reason why they don't show up is because the Hero pick screen is ignoring the "override_hero" key
you'll need to go through your hero definitions and rename them to the default Hero, so, in my case: "npc_dota_hero_rai" { "AbilityLayout" "4" "HeroSelectSoundEffect" "Hero_Zuus.LightningBolt" "Role" "Escape,Nuker" ... etc becomes "npc_dota_hero_ember_spirit" { "AbilityLayout" "4" "HeroSelectSoundEffect" "Hero_Zuus.LightningBolt" "Role" "Escape,Nuker" ... etc
that will fully override them and show custom abilites/talents
hope that helps
